### 11.2 Blueprint — KHÔNG cần tạo mới

`system_extract_blueprint_mystery.txt` đã tồn tại. Logic differences:
- Review: input text chứa 7-12 mysteries → blueprint có 7-12 `product_evaluation` entries
- Narrative: input text chứa 1 mystery → blueprint có 1 `product_evaluation` entry (with richer detail)
- Blueprint extractor tự adapt vì nó extract "whatever is in the text"

